            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-img">
            <div class="img-2"></div>
            <h3>AI Strategy</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="card-text">
            <p>
              Define a clear and effective AI roadmap aligned with business
              goals.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-img">
            <div class="img-3"></div>
            <h3>Custom AI Tools</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="card-text">
            <p>Build tailored AI tools designed specifically for your needs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY CHOOSE US -->
  <section>
    <div class="container why">
      <h2 class="section-title">Why Choose Us</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <div class="tick">✔</div>
          <p>AI-First Approach</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="tick">✔</div>
          <p>Fast Turnaround</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="tick">✔</div>
          <p>Secure & Ethical AI</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

